---

<Layout
  title={pageTitle}
  description={pageDescription}
  canonical="/"
  ogImage={ogImage}
  ogImageAlt="Phil Reese, Arizona Business Broker"
  ogImageWidth={1200}
  ogImageHeight={1200}
  structuredData={structuredData}
>
  <!-- lite-youtube web component (paulirish/lite-youtube-embed) — replaces the
       live site's wp-youtube-lyte lazy embed. Thumbnail + play button render
       instantly; the YouTube iframe loads only on click. -->
  <link
    slot="head"
    rel="stylesheet"
    href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/lite-youtube-embed@0.3.2/src/lite-yt-embed.css"
  />
  <script
    slot="head"
    is:inline
    src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/lite-youtube-embed@0.3.2/src/lite-yt-embed.js"
    defer></script>

  <!-- 1. banner-sctn — light text banner ("hero": no photo on live) -->
  <section class="section banner-sctn">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <div class="one-col">
        <h1 class="maintitle h1-style">Thinking About Selling Your AZ Business?</h1>
        <h2 class="subtitle h5-style">Find Out What It’s Really Worth. Confidentially &amp; At No Cost.</h2>
        <p>I help Arizona business owners sell their companies quietly, at the right time, and for the best possible price. I have over 20 years of experience working directly with business owners. When you work with me, I can assure you there will be no pressure, no gimmicks, and no surprises</p>
        <h3 class="sbtext h4-style">I Have Personally Closed Over 97 Million Dollars in Business Sales Across 100+ Transactions</h3>
        <div class="bnr-inn">
          <div>
            <Fragment set:html={googleGLogoSvg} />
            <span class="strs">★★★★★</span>
          </div>
          <img src="/images/bbb-accredited.png" alt="BBB Accredited Business A+" width="187" height="47" class="alignnone size-full" />
        </div>
        <div class="badgess-inn">
          <div class="certified-badges">
            <div class="wth-svg" set:html={ibbaBadgeSvg} />
            <div><img src="/images/badge-azbba.png" width="74" height="73" alt="AZBBA logo" /></div>
            <div><img src="/images/badge-cbi.png" alt="CBI Badge" width="164" height="162" class="alignnone size-full" /></div>
            <div><img src="/images/badge-top1percent-2025.png" alt="" width="70" height="88" class="alignnone size-full" /></div>
            <div><img src="/images/badge-multimillion-2025.png" alt="" width="80" height="80" class="alignnone size-full" /></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 2. phil-sctn — Meet Phil -->
  <section class="section phil-sctn">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <div class="img-col">
        <img
          fetchpriority="high"
          src="/images/home/phil-reese-portrait.png"
          alt=""
          width="417"
          height="588"
          class="alignnone size-full"
          srcset="/images/home/phil-reese-portrait.png 417w, /images/home/phil-reese-portrait-213x300.png 213w"
          sizes="(max-width: 417px) 100vw, 417px"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="txt-col">
        <h3 class="maintitle h3-style">Phil Reese</h3>
        <p>Selling a business is personal. I know because I’ve been in your shoes. In 1995, I co-founded First Impression Security Doors out of my garage in Mesa, growing it to a full manufacturing facility in Gilbert with 13 employees before a successful exit in 2001. That company has since grown into Arizona’s largest ornamental iron firm.</p>
        <p>Today, I use my over 20 years of Business Brokering expertise to help owners navigate their own exits. I am one of only four business brokers in the state to hold the Master Certified Business Intermediary (MCBI) designation. As the former Ethics Chairman for the Arizona Business Brokers Association (AZBBA), I prioritize confidentiality and integrity throughout the whole sales process, ensuring your legacy is protected.</p>
        <div class="btns btns-alt">
          <a href="/about/">Learn More About Phil</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 3. sold-sctn — Businesses sold -->
  <section class="section sold-sctn">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <div class="title-col">
        <h3 class="maintitle h3-style">Some of the Businesses I have sold</h3>
      </div>
      {soldCols.map((col) => (
        <div class="sold-col">
          <h4 class="subtitle h4-style">{col.headline} <span>{col.type}</span></h4>
          <ul>
            {col.items.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
          </ul>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 4. infogrhp-sctn — Selling process infographic -->
  <section class="section infogrhp-sctn">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <div class="title-col">
        <h3 class="maintitle h3-style">The Process Of Selling Your Arizona Business <span>Step-By-Step</span> </h3>
        <div class="spt"></div>
      </div>
      <a class="desk-imgcol" href="/contact/">
        <span class="stpone">Step One</span>
        <img
          src="/images/home/selling-process-infographic.svg"
          alt=""
          width="834"
          height="875"
          class="alignnone size-full"
          loading="lazy"
          role="img"
        />
      </a>
      <ul class="mob-steps">
        <li class="stp-box">
          <p>Step One <br />Contact Phil</p>
        </li>
        <li class="stp-box">
          <p>He’ll Determine the Value of Your Business</p>
        </li>
        <li class="spt2" set:html={sptDividerSvg} />
        <li class="stp-box">
          <p>List Your Business</p>
        </li>
        <li class="stp-box">
          <p>Go To Market</p>
        </li>
        <li class="spt2" set:html={sptDividerSvg} />
        <li class="stp-box">
          <p>Screen Business Buyer Candidates</p>
        </li>
        <li class="stp-box">
          <p>Buyer &amp; Seller Meeting</p>
        </li>
        <li class="spt2" set:html={sptDividerSvg} />
        <li class="stp-box">
          <p>Buyer Makes An Offer</p>
        </li>
        <li class="stp-box">
          <p>Buyer Does Due Diligence</p>
        </li>
        <li class="spt2" set:html={sptDividerSvg} />
        <li class="stp-box">
          <p>Close on The Sale</p>
        </li>
        <li class="stp-box">
          <p>Buyer Starts the Training Process</p>
        </li>
        <li class="stp-box btns btns-alt">
          <a href="/contact/">Contact Phil</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 5. vid-sctn — Valuation video -->
  <section class="section vid-sctn">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <div class="vid-col">
        <div class="lyte-wrapper" style="width:853px;max-width:100%;margin:5px;">
          <lite-youtube
            videoid="ajTOke4_h9A"
            title="Watch this Video to See How I Go About Determining the Value of Your Business"
            style="background-image:url('/images/home/video-poster-ajTOke4_h9A.jpg');"
          >
            <a href="https://youtu.be/ajTOke4_h9A" class="lite-yt-fallback" rel="nofollow">Watch this video on YouTube</a>
          </lite-youtube>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="titlecol">
        <h3 class="maintitle h3-style">Watch this Video to See How I Go About Determining the Value of Your Business</h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 6. test-sctn — Testimonials -->
  <section class="section test-sctn">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <div class="title-col">
        <h3 class="subtitle h3-style">Read What My Past Clients Have Said</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="google-col">
        <Fragment set:html={googleGLogoSvg} />
        <div>
          <p>Over 60 reviews</p>
          <span>5.0 <span class="strs">★★★★★</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="main-rvw">
        <p>Working with Phil Reese was truly an exceptional experience! From the very first consultation to the final closing, Phil went above and beyond to make selling my business smooth, stress-free, and successful. His expertise in the Arizona market is unmatched — he knew exactly how to position my business to attract the right buyers and negotiated a deal that exceeded my expectations.</p>
        <p>Phil is incredibly professional, responsive, and genuinely cares about his clients. He took the time to answer all my questions, kept me updated every step of the way, and always made me feel like a top priority. His honesty and integrity gave me complete peace of mind throughout the entire process.</p>
        <p>If you are considering selling or buying a business in Arizona, I cannot recommend Phil Reese enough. He is hands down the best business broker out there — knowledgeable, dedicated, and a true partner you can trust. Thank you, Phil, for helping me achieve my goals and making this such a positive experience!</p>
        <p class="name">Rickey Woolfolk <span class="strs">★★★★★</span></p>
        <p class="biz-main">Empower Academy</p>
        <p><a class="rvw-link" href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/gQ4DHB1MjVPDqCKB9" target="_blank">Reposted from Google</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="rvw-box">
        <p>Words alone can not describe how professional and knowledgeable Phil is when it comes to selling a business.  After my husband and I decided to sell our company we interviewed Phil and knew right away that he was our guy!!   Being once a business owner himself he knew all of our concerns and questions.  Phil guided us through the entire process from listing, advertising to closing.<br />  Not only did Phil sell our company quicker than we expected he also got us FULL PRICE!!!   Can’t Thank him enough!!!</p>
        <a class="rvw-link" href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/PravqkfmGsH2HM3d8" target="_blank">Reposted from Google</a>
        <div class="rvw-bx">
          <img src="/images/home/avatar-liz-majerczyk.png" alt="" width="72" height="72" class="alignnone size-full" loading="lazy" />
          <div>
            <p class="bss-name">Liz Majerczyk</p>
            <p class="name">Vent Masters</p>
            <span class="strs">★★★★★</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rvw-box">
        <p>We had owned our business for over 30 years and it was time to sell our business and retire. We were entrusting our life’s work to someone we didn’t know and we were very nervous, therefore, we did a lot of research on brokers as it was imperative that this person be experienced, knowledgeable and reliable.  It  was a complicated process but Phil was determined to get us the best deal possible, regardless of how much time and work was involved.   He worked tirelessly day and night to get it done, and done right; he definitely earned his commission.  We are grateful to Phil for everything he did for us and strongly recommend him to sell your business.</p>
        <a class="rvw-link" href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/NWEg4mgR83xtb9rn7" target="_blank">Reposted from Google</a>
        <div class="rvw-bx">
          <img src="/images/home/avatar-debbie-thompson.png" alt="" width="72" height="72" class="alignnone size-full" loading="lazy" />
          <div>
            <p class="bss-name">Debbie Thompson</p>
            <p class="name">First Impressions Dental Lab</p>
